This is a brand page for the FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS trademark by FFC Capital Advisors, LLC 
                                in New Orleans, LA, 70130.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner FFC Capital Advisors, LLC of the FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS trademark.
                           






On Friday, April 27, 2012,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS by 
                        FFC Capital Advisors, LLC, New Orleans, LA  70130.
                        The USPTO has given the FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS 
                        trademark serial  number of  85610669.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS is 
                        
                        
                                            FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS, LLC of 
                                            400 POYDRAS ST # 2430,  NEW ORLEANS, LA 70130-3245,  
                                .
                            The FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for FFC CAPITAL ADVISORS 
                            is Advice relating to investments; Brokerage services for capital investments; Capital investment consulting; Financial advisory and consultancy services; Financial and investment services, namely, management and brokerage in the fields of stocks, bonds, options, commodities, futures and other securities, and the investment of funds of others; Financial investment analysis and stock research; Financial investment brokerage services; Financial investment services, namely, administering the issuance, underwriting and distribution of securities; Investment banking services. 
                            





