For private investors who want to delegate decision making to a trusted experienced fiduciary, we offer truly customized, independent solutions that prioritize your objectives.

Key benefits:


You set your specific investment objectives, risk tolerances, and tax strategies 
We implement your portfolio and administration so you do not have to
You have daily access to accounting and performance measurement 
We are available anytime you have questions or want to discuss your portfolio 

*Fiduciary custodial services are provided by Pershing Advisor
 Solutions, LLC; a Bank of New York Mellon company.


Traditional Brokerage Products and Services 

FFC Capital Advisors also offers a variety of traditional brokerage products and services that include:


Stocks, Bonds
Retirement Planning ---------- Learn More >>
Wealth & Estate Planning 
Variable Annuities & Life Insurance
Exchange Traded Funds, Mutual Funds 


Wrap Fee Programs 

Our wrap fee program alternatives enable clients to engage in consolidated investment management and consulting services that might otherwise be logistically and cost prohibitive. 
 


Ultra Sigma® - Total Portfolio Series (TPS™)
“TPS” is a discretionary broad based asset allocation driven wrap fee program; specifically designed for customers that are interested in achieving broad market exposure to growth, income and alternatives.  


Ultra Sigma® - All-Cap Equity Series (Global ACES™) 
“ACES” is a discretionary equity only, global, all capitalization wrap fee program; specifically designed for customers that are interested in achieving broad market exposure to growth and alternatives. 


Ultra Sigma® - Liquidity Management Series (LMS™) 
“LMS” is a discretionary short to intermediate term fixed income derivative wrap fee program; specifically designed for customers that are interested in achieving income, safety, and liquidity. 





























