Individuals

From private banking ... to wealth & retirement 
planning ... to investment management services; We work 
collaboratively with you to create and execute customized 
financial strategies to help achieve your goals.




Institutions 

From pension & investment advisory ... to investment

banking & market access ... We support both public and 
private institutions to finance capital projects, manage 
short-term assets & long-term liabilities and more.





















Welcome!

FFC Capital Markets® is a securities and investment banking firm that provides a range of financial services. Founded in 2001, we are headquartered in New Orleans and maintain regional offices
 in Opelousas, LA and Jackson, MS. 
Our mission is to be a trusted financial partner to critically accountable institutions and private investors alike. For nearly 30 years, we have been at the vanguard of the investment management
 business allowing us to know exactly what it takes to build and maintain critically accountable, liability-driven institutional investments. We use that expertise to intelligently engineer customized solutions designed to maximize your investment results within
 the constraints of your unique risk profile.
FFC Capital Markets®  offers advisory consulting services through
FFC Capital Management (FFCCM,) a SEC Registered Investment Adviser (RIA) and a SEC Registered Municipal Advisor (MA) and offers securities through FFC Capital Advisors
(FFCCA,) LLC a full service broker dealer, Member FINRA & SIPC.



Learn More

























